{
  "description": "The image captures a powerful waterfall cascading down a sheer granite cliff face. The waterfall is partially obscured by mist and spray, creating a dynamic and ethereal effect. In the foreground, large, dark rocks are scattered throughout a rushing stream of water, suggesting a rocky riverbed. The cliff face is massive and textured, with visible lines and crevices indicative of geological formations. Sparse vegetation clings to the cliff's sides, adding a touch of green to the otherwise grey and white landscape. The overall scene evokes a sense of natural power and scale.",
